== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2015年8月，宣佈[[獅門|獅門]]正在製作一部改編自《[[邊緣禁地系列|邊緣禁地系列]]》的電影，由阿里·阿拉德和{{le|阿維·阿拉德|Avi Arad}}擔任製片人<ref>{{cite web |last=McNary |first=Dave |date=2015-08-28 |title='Borderlands' Videogame Movie in Works at Lionsgate |url=https://variety.com/2015/film/news/borderlands-videogame-movie-lionsgate-1201580303/ |access-date=2021-01-27 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029151741/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/borderlands-videogame-movie-lionsgate-1201580303/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年2月，宣佈該片將由[[艾利·羅斯|艾利·羅斯]]執導，{{le|克雷格·麥辛|Craig Mazin}}編劇<ref>{{cite web |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |date=2020-02-20 |title=Eli Roth To Direct Adaptation Of Sci-Fi Videogame 'Borderlands' For Lionsgate |url=https://deadline.com/2020/02/borderlands-videogame-eli-roth-directing-lionsgate-movie-1202864502/ |access-date=2021-01-27 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |archive-date=2020-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224212648/https://deadline.com/2020/02/borderlands-videogame-eli-roth-directing-lionsgate-movie-1202864502/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月，[[凱特·布蘭琪|凱特·布蘭琪]]為飾演角色莉莉絲進行洽談，並於同月底確認出演電影<ref>{{cite web |last=N'Duka |first=Amanda |date=2020-05-05 |title=Oscar Winner Cate Blanchett In Talks To Join 'Borderlands' Adaptation At Lionsgate |url=https://deadline.com/2020/05/cate-blanchett-borderlands-lionsgate-1202926685/ |access-date=2021-01-27 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815152347/https://deadline.com/2020/05/cate-blanchett-borderlands-lionsgate-1202926685/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Romano |first=Nick |date=2020-05-28 |title=Cate Blanchett to star in Eli Roth's Borderlands movie |url=https://ew.com/movies/cate-blanchett-borderlands/ |access-date=2021-01-27 |website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20