/deadline.com/2021/02/jamie-lee-curtis-cate-blanchett-kevin-hart-borderlands-lionsgate-1234689764/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=N'Duka |first=Amanda |date=2021-02-11 |title=Jack Black Reunites With Eli Roth & Cate Blanchett For 'Borderlands' Movie |url=https://deadline.com/2021/02/jack-black-eli-roth-cate-blanchett-borderlands-lionsgate-1234692217/ |access-date=2021-02-11 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |archive-date=2022-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220213133346/https://deadline.com/2021/02/jack-black-eli-roth-cate-blanchett-borderlands-lionsgate-1234692217/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月，雅瑞安娜·葛林布雷、[[佛洛里安·蒙特亞努|佛洛里安·蒙特亞努]]和[[海莉·班奈特|海莉·班奈特]]加盟演員陣容<ref>{{cite web |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=2021-03-01 |title=Young Gamora Actress Ariana Greenblatt Joins Cate Blanchett, Kevin Hart in 'Borderlands' Movie |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/young-gamora-actress-ariana-greenblatt-joins-cate-blanchett-kevin-hart-in-borderlands-movie |access-date=2021-03-01 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301201110/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/young-gamora-actress-ariana-greenblatt-joins-cate-blanchett-kevin-hart-in-borderlands-movie |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=2021-03-09 |title='Creed II' Actor Florian Munteanu Joining Cate Blanchett, Kevin Hart in 'Borderlands' Movie (Exclusive) |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/creed-ii-actor-florian-munteanu-joining-cate-blanchett-kevin-hart-in-borderlands-movie-exclusive |access-date=2021-03-09 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |archive-date=2021-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310055036/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/creed-ii-actor-florian-munteanu-joining-cate-blanchett-kevin-hart-in-borderlands-movie-exclusive |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |date=2021-03-12 |title=Haley Bennett To Star In Eli Roth's 'Borderlands' |url=https://deadline.com/2021/03/haley-bennett-to-star-in-eli-roths-borderlands-1234713251/ |access-date=2021-03-12 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |archive-date=2021-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420222705/https://deadline.com/2021/03/haley-bennett-to-star-in-eli-roths-borderlands-1234713251/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

